This hook runs `gitleaks git --no-banner --redact -l warn` before push. It is intentionally broader than the pre-commit hook: pre-commit checks staged content, while pre-push scans full git history, including refs/notes/*.

In this repo, tracked hooks under `hooks/` are active because `core.hooksPath=hooks/`.
